# My API

Defines a validation schema for the HTTP message-body with Schema keyword.

# Create user [POST /user]

+ Request (application/json)
    + Attributes
        + name: John (string, required) - User name
        + email: `admin@localhost` (string, optional)

    + Schema

            {
                "$schema": "http://json-schema.org/draft-04/schema#",
                "type": "object",
                "properties": {
                    "name": {
                        "type": "string"
                    },
                    "msisdn": {
                        "type": "string"
                    }
                }
            }

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes
        + status: `ok`

    + Schema

            {
                "$schema": "http://json-schema.org/draft-04/schema#",
                "type": "object",
                "properties": {
                    "status": {
                        "type": "string",
                        "enum": [
                            "ok"
                        ]
                    }
                },
                "required": [
                    "status"
                ]
            }
